TITLE: Implementing Temperature Converter State Machine with XState in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet creates an XState machine for a temperature converter. It handles conversion between Celsius and Fahrenheit, updating both values simultaneously when either input changes. The machine has a single 'active' state and uses context to store temperature values.
