TITLE: Restoring Persisted State in XState v5
DESCRIPTION: Restoring persisted state is now done by passing the state into the 'snapshot' property of the 'createActor' options argument. The persisted snapshot is obtained from an actor by calling 'actor.getPersistedSnapshot()'.
