LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
type TimerEvent =
  | {
      // The TICK event sent by the spawned interval service
      type: 'TICK';
    }
  | {
      // User intent to update the duration
      type: 'DURATION.UPDATE';
      value: number;
    }
  | {
      // User intent to reset the elapsed time to 0
      type: 'RESET';
    };
```

